FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  7 AND t.production_year  >  1968 AND ci.person_id  >  1674218 AND ci.role_id  <  5 AND mk.keyword_id  >  2039
